      <title>Simplify Azure Management Group Setup using Bicep Vending</title>
      <link>https://www.devjev.nl/posts/2025/simplify-azure-management-group-setup-using-bicep-vending/</link>
      <pubDate>Tue, 07 Jan 2025 02:00:00 +0200</pubDate>
